dj2.quest.db.655.title=全是数字!
dj2.quest.db.655.desc=现在你已经有了惧质水晶...你已经很强大了.你可以选择用这个水晶开启血魔法,或是制作最强大的采矿机:数字采矿机!%n%n如果你选择了后者,这里是它的简易使用说明:%n%n在它的GUI中,你可以看到一个配置按钮,可以用来指定:%n%n-其挖掘半径,最大32格,%n-你想要开采的Y轴范围.%n-你想要挖掘什么(你会需要添加一个过滤标签).
dj2.quest.db.656.title=捕获太阳的能量
dj2.quest.db.656.desc=不需要再去金星了!我们会用植物代替!
dj2.quest.db.657.title=新大陆?
dj2.quest.db.657.desc=通过横跨大西洋来发现欧洲-我是说分解一些空间碎片来发现铕!
dj2.quest.db.658.title=分解
dj2.quest.db.658.desc=这些元素似乎在高放射性分维化合物中疯狂地移动着!把它分解为这些(新)元素!
dj2.quest.db.659.title=但其他国家呢?!
dj2.quest.db.659.desc=一个很有趣的巧合,铕(Europium)原子序数的一半(几乎)恰好是锗(Germanium)的原子序数...!
dj2.quest.db.660.title=史诗说唱战!!-ium
dj2.quest.db.660.desc=希望你已经找到了熔融恒星合金的来源.你会需要很多!%n%n(译注:铒erbium 任务名Epic Rap Battles -ium 缩写erbium)
dj2.quest.db.661.title=别告诉你的元素们这件事
dj2.quest.db.661.desc=将你的钅卢分解为碲!%n%n(译注:该元素单字无法显示,故拆分显示,非汉化错误)
dj2.quest.db.662.title=排列,变化,组合!
dj2.quest.db.662.desc=你迄今为止最伟大的壮举!你成功找到了一种能将铒,镓,碲,聚氯乙烯和磷酸氢二铵结合成稳定化合物的方法...
dj2.quest.db.663.title=组合不要停!
dj2.quest.db.663.desc=将镎,锗,丁烷和酰胺结合在一起,看看会变成什么...!
dj2.quest.db.664.title=拼写大赛的噩梦
dj2.quest.db.664.desc=之前从未见过这种化合物... %n%n%n%n它有如此美丽的粉红色调.... %n%n%n%n而且...%n%n%n等等...%n%n%n???%n%n%n不,这不可能.%n%n%n这种材料会让炼金术的转化简单得多....%n%n%n%n%n...%n%n%n%n§l%n我%n%n到底%n%n创造了%n%n什么?!
dj2.quest.db.665.title=它会在被倒出后凝固...
dj2.quest.db.665.desc=并且它会形成水晶结构...非常奇特.
dj2.quest.db.666.title=哦,NCC不会让我这样
dj2.quest.db.666.desc=Neodymit Calcium Carbonate.你以为NCC是什么?%n%n%n不管怎样.%n%n%n分解一些共价粉.再把产物继续分解为钕.
dj2.quest.db.667.title=从粉,到粉,再到粉
dj2.quest.db.667.desc=组合其它奇点来制作热力粉尘奇点,然后制作你的第一批低等共价粉!
dj2.quest.db.668.title=锻造水晶与灵魂
dj2.quest.db.668.desc=将G.E.R.C.水晶与我之前得到的灵魂锻造在一起,我得到了一个僵硬但充满活力的神奇结构.它其上跃动着地量,就像准备好要把世界天翻地覆一样.
dj2.quest.db.669.title=Boom Boom Pow
dj2.quest.db.669.desc=I like that Boom Boom Pow%nThem essence flying to 'sky%nIt's tryna blow up and fly%nI'm gonna stop it now!%n%nI'm making coffee and cake%nThis is just blowin' all day%nIt's got that Boom Boom Boom%nKeeps going Boom Boom Boom%nLet me get it now%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%nI'm so 3008, you're so 200-late! (Huh, destroyed!)%n%n(译注:Black Eyed Peas-Boom Boom Pow)
dj2.quest.db.670.title=发现新大-我是说新元素
dj2.quest.db.670.desc=分解红物质来获取镅!%n%n结合你现在所有的力量,制作一个中子态素压缩机!
dj2.quest.db.671.title=真正的EMC
dj2.quest.db.671.desc=从你的转化桌中获取EMC.你需要至少填入16,777,216(即2^24)EMC才能看到这个转化.
dj2.quest.db.672.title=更蓝的蓝
dj2.quest.db.672.desc=将中等共价粉,炼金奇点和暗物质结合为高等共价粉!
dj2.quest.db.673.title=天蓝色
dj2.quest.db.673.desc=将所有EnderIO管道拓展的奇点结合为一个,然后制作一些中等共价粉!
dj2.quest.db.674.title=呆在在EMC-A太有趣了!
dj2.quest.db.674.desc=通过潜行左击将炼金术秘卷放入转化桌!转化桌将显示"Learned!"然后把任何有EMC值的物品放进去.所有可以用EMC制造的物品都会显示出来.%n%n最好用的材料是虚空金属锭.由于它们的原始制作方法非常昂贵,所以它们含有大量的EMC.然而,因为你有虚空金属种子,所以你可以免费获得它们.%n%nProjectE主要用于替换你的落后的农场,刷怪场和采石场,而且可以让你只用继续运营一个农场(虚空金属作物农场),这样你的游戏就不会再那么卡了.以后你甚至可以直接从光中产生EMC,所以你可能连这一种农场都不需要了.%n%n暗物质需要100多万EMC(准确来讲,是2^20EMC)来创造,你只需要消耗40个虚空金属锭.做一点暗物质吧!%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%nIt's fun to stay at the EMC-A!%nIt's fun to stay at the EMC-A!%n%nThey have everything for you men to enjoy%nYou can hang out with all the boys%n%nIt's fun to stay at the EMC-A!%nIt's fun to stay at the EMC-A!%n%nYou can get yourself clean, you can have a good meal%nYou can have all the resources you need%n%n(译注:Village People-YMCA)
dj2.quest.db.675.title=氪金货币
dj2.quest.db.675.desc=将铪分解为氪,并制作一些氪灯!%n%n%n为安全起见,别让超人碰这些.
dj2.quest.db.676.title=半-金属,铪
dj2.quest.db.676.desc=从高等共价粉或暗物质中制作硫化铪.因为你可以用EMC创造暗物质,所以暗物质可能会是更好的选择.
dj2.quest.db.677.title=不再有EMC问题
dj2.quest.db.677.desc=制作能量收集器!这台机器可以在光照等级15的地方以每秒产生12EMC的速度被动生产最高30,000EMC.
dj2.quest.db.678.title=如何避免EMC危机
dj2.quest.db.678.desc=制作一个能量收集器MK1,它能将光转化为EMC!当在最高光照强度下,它每秒钟会产生4EMC,上限为10,000EMC.当将其放置在能量凝聚器或反物质继电器旁时,它能将EMC转移到该机器中.
dj2.quest.db.679.title=读书学习,孩子!
dj2.quest.db.679.desc=将炼金化学mod的奇点结合为炼金奇点,然后制作一本炼金术秘卷.
dj2.quest.db.680.title=全部变成金
dj2.quest.db.680.desc=将所有科技相关节点结合来制作科技节点!%n%n然后制作转化桌!请注意,贤者之石是在制作转化桌的时候消耗掉的!
dj2.quest.db.681.title=物质分解
dj2.quest.db.681.desc=分解你的暗物质来获取氡和钋!
dj2.quest.db.682.title=我确信它会合适
dj2.quest.db.682.desc=制作一个能量凝聚器!这个机器可以:%n%n-将放置在其中的任意物品转化为EMC,这些EMC将存储在其内部缓存里.%n%n-从相邻的能量收集器或反物质中继器中接收EMC.%n%n-使用其内部缓存中的EMC制造指定物品.
dj2.quest.db.683.title=这只是个精致的箱子.
dj2.quest.db.683.desc=从高放射性分维化合物中获取镎.%n%n然后用你最珍贵的材料来制作你的第一个炼金术箱子!这是所有自动EMC转化凝聚器的合成材料.
dj2.quest.db.684.title=镝
dj2.quest.db.684.desc=将一些中等共价尘分解为镝!
dj2.quest.db.685.title=气氢
dj2.quest.db.685.desc=!氢反造创来变聚弱用
dj2.quest.db.686.title=质物的要重
dj2.quest.db.686.desc=!电反和子子质反为化转们它将来质物反态液点倒上子电和子质往
dj2.quest.db.687.title=重要的物质
dj2.quest.db.687.desc=钋在裂变仓中被转化为钼.但在弱聚变中,它可以帮助一个氢原子分解为一个质子和一个电子!%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%nCERN就是这么做的.相信我.你没必要去查证.
dj2.quest.db.688.title=建立EMC系统
dj2.quest.db.688.desc=制作能量收集器ME3!在强光下或放置在地狱中时,它将会每秒被动产生40EMC,上限为60,000EMC.
dj2.quest.db.689.title=腐化
dj2.quest.db.689.desc=在世界中使用贤者之石将觉醒龙块转化为腐化龙块.%n%n当你制造了第二块贤者之石后,你可以用它和方块放置器/采掘器(或成型/破坏面板,或方块放置口/破坏口)和一个使用者/玩家模拟器设置腐化龙块的自动化.
dj2.quest.db.690.title=全金属
dj2.quest.db.690.desc=将氡进一步分解为锝,并将其转化为"全金属"形态!%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n是的,一个小小的梗,我知道.%n%n(译注:fullmetal)
dj2.quest.db.691.title=光速,平方
dj2.quest.db.691.desc=将你的反物质继电器一路升级至MK3!当传输EMC时,它会提供10EMC/s的额外EMC,使它在动力花设计中真正可行.它可以传输多达640EMC/s,并可存储10,000,000EMC.%n%n动力花的设置包括一个位于中心的能量凝聚器MK2,除顶部外侧面的5个反物质继电器(这样中心的凝聚器仍然能被访问),然后用能量收集器包围整个设备,最后在外侧放置萤石.%n%n这将生产EMC并输送至中心的能量凝聚器,以使用光创造任何你想要的物品!好耶!
dj2.quest.db.692.title=如何平方你的资源
dj2.quest.db.692.desc=将你的反物质继电器升级为反物质继电器MK2.当传输时,它会提供3EMC/s的加成.它最大可以传输192EMC/s并可存储最高1,000,000EMC.
dj2.quest.db.693.title=不要冷却.让它发热吧!
dj2.quest.db.693.desc=制作裂变催化剂!用它替换裂变冷却剂来获得一些...意外结果.
dj2.quest.db.694.title=确保长出反重力的手
dj2.quest.db.694.desc=100个反氢可以制作一个反物质簇...让它流动起来,因为不这样的话,如果它碰到普通物质的话...%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n就会爆炸.%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n*并不会真的爆炸,只是背景叙述而已.别太担心.
dj2.quest.db.695.title=E[MC] §r=§r [E]MC^2
dj2.quest.db.695.desc=制作反物质继电器MK1.这台机器有两个功能.首先,它能将放置于其中的物品转化为EMC.其次,它能将能量收集器中的能量转移至能量凝聚器中.%n%n转移能量时,它会提供一个1EMC每秒的能量加成.它也可以被用来向卡莱恩能量之星中注入能量.%n%n它可以最大传输64EMC/s并可存储高达100,000EMC.
dj2.quest.db.696.title=全部塞进去
dj2.quest.db.696.desc=能量凝聚器MK2是能量凝聚器的升级版本.它除了比能量凝聚器快得多之外,他还有一个单独的输出物品栏.物品只能从输出侧提取并从输入侧输入.
dj2.quest.db.697.title=哲学
dj2.quest.db.697.desc=制作右边列出的五种组合奇点,并再次将它们组合成魔法奇点!%n%n制作一些天体晶核.这次它们需要用天体水晶石制作,水晶石至少要有700的尺寸和75%的纯度.你应该像自动处理水晶石一样自动处理它们.记住要制作天体水晶,你只需要把一个水晶石和一个星尘扔入星能液之中.等到水晶长大,再将其打碎.%n%n然而自动天体水晶的方式与自动水晶石完全相同,因为天体水晶也可以分裂.Direwolf20的视频 "Enigmatica 2 Ep88 Dynamics Crystal Growth Pt2"(链接:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8F3K8sSN3aM)仍是这一自动化过程的一个极好的例子.%n%n最后,当你完成了这些所有先决条件后,制作一块贤者之石.
dj2.quest.db.698.title=大突破!大突破!
dj2.quest.db.698.desc=TNT也可以压缩.是的.这是一个常规的Minecraft专家包,你在期待些什么?它不能被压缩成一个奇点吗?
dj2.quest.db.699.title=结果到头来那根本不重要
dj2.quest.db.699.desc=使用默认为'V'的充能键为其充能,并毁灭所有物质!那根本不重要!%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%nI TRIED SO HARD AND GOT SO FAR!%nBUT IN THE END IT DOESN'T EVEN MATTER!%nI HAD TO FALL TO LOSE IT ALLLL!%nBUT IN THE END IT DOESN'T EVEN MATTER-ER-eeer!%n%n(译注:In the end-林肯公园)
dj2.quest.db.700.title=WayOfTime的灵感
dj2.quest.db.700.desc=制作右边列出的每一种红物质工具!%n%n你可以使用ProjectE的充能键(默认为'V')来为这些工具充能以获得特殊效果:%n%n-红物质镐可以通过右击破坏相连的多达32块同种方块.如果你在不是矿石的方块上使用它,它会扫描该区域的矿石,并对最近的一块矿石使用该能力.%n%n-红物质铲会根据其充能等级挖掘一个范围内的方块.它需要由卡莱恩能量之星或炼金燃料提供EMC.%n%n-红物质锤会在一个更大的范围内摧毁方块,但你只能在石头类的方块上使用它.它需要由卡莱恩能量之星或炼金燃料提供EMC.
dj2.quest.db.701.title=和平主义的道德观
dj2.quest.db.701.desc=制作右边列出的每一种红物质工具!%n%n你可以使用ProjectE的充能键(默认为'V')来为这些工具充能以获得特殊效果.%n%n-红物质剑可以消耗玩家物品栏内的萤石粉来进行一次范围攻击.%n%n-红物质斧会消耗红石粉在与其充能等级成比例的范围内破坏所有木头.%n%n-红物质锄将会耕更大范围的地.%n%n-红物质剪刀会使羊掉落8个羊毛而非1-3个.不幸的是,这也会对羊群造成伤害.然而,它也将有很小的概率会克隆羊.你也可以在树附近使用它,将会掉落附近的所有的树叶块.%n
dj2.quest.db.702.title=感受力量
dj2.quest.db.702.desc=制作两个来自ProjectE的全能工具!%n%n红物质拳剑结合了红物质剑,锄头,斧子和剪刀.随着充能等级的提升,它的速度也会得到提升.这也会影响它的所有能力,例如其伤害和作用范围.它还可以剪羊或蘑菇牛,并且有一定概率克隆它们.按工具的使用键可以破坏区域内所有原木和树叶,对草地使用会耕完区域内的所有土地.%n%n松开充能键将杀死这片区域内所有生物.它将杀死地狱中所有的僵尸猪人群.它具体是杀死所有生物还是敌对生物取决于其所处模式.%n%n红物质钉头锤结合了红物质锤,镐和铲.它也可以用于快速破坏木头类型的方块,但不能使用红物质斧那种对木头起效的能力.当使用时,他可以挖出一个大的立方体区域的石头类方块或挖掉一层平坦的土类方块,与其充电水平相关.
dj2.quest.db.703.title=律法之刃
dj2.quest.db.703.desc=鬼哭.%n%n律法之刃.%n%n诅咒之刃.%n%n无限耐久.%n%n击杀创造.%n%n穿透护甲.%n%n它可以被赋予任何附魔,最高达附魔上限的两倍,在铁砧上组合附魔会将等级相加.你不再需要两个锋利III来获取锋利IV,你只需要一个锋利III和一个锋利I.%n%nOP吗?%n%n确实.%n%n当之无愧?%n%n肯定的.
dj2.quest.db.704.title=其他的都不重要
dj2.quest.db.704.desc=向你的转化桌内填入至少268,435,456(即2^28)EMC来获取白物质.%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%nSo close, no matter how faaaar%nCouldn't be much more from the heaaaart%nForever trusting who we aaaare%nAnd nothing else matteeeeers%n%nNever opened myself this waaaay%nLife is ours, we live it our waaaaay%nAll these words, I don't just saaaaay%nAnd nothing else matteeeeers%n%n(译注:METALLICA-Nothing else matters)
dj2.quest.db.705.title=这是时间问题
dj2.quest.db.705.desc=T时间洪流怀表是个非常强大的物品,它可以加快附近方块的时间流速.按ProjectE充能键(默认为V)来为其充能,当它在你的快捷栏中时,它会加速一天的流逝.%n%n它有两个模式-加速或逆转一天的时间!右键点击来切换"关闭","加速"和"倒退"模式.%n%n更重要的是,当把它放置在已激活的暗物质台座上时,它会18倍加速4个方块范围内的所有方块的游戏刻.你可以空手右击暗物质台座来激活它.%n如果你在服务器中游玩,不用太惊讶这个东西会被禁用掉...%n
dj2.quest.db.706.title=带走我的呼吸
dj2.quest.db.706.desc=黑暗领域是创造反空气的完美地点...是的!这种空气,完全由反粒子组成,比如反氮,反氧和反二氧...! ...等等.它确实是这样的,对吧?%n%n%n总之!做一点!
dj2.quest.db.707.title=游说中心
dj2.quest.db.707.desc=欢迎来到创造阶段!首先,如果你还没做死亡庇护巫毒娃娃的自动化,你应该先做完它.然后制作几个堕落核心!你最后会需要更多,但现在两个就够了.
dj2.quest.db.708.title=毁灭的鬼魂
dj2.quest.db.708.desc=ᚥᚼᛊᚨᛗᛞᚠ! ᚠᚼᚼᚼᛊ, ᚢᛤᚢᛤᚢᛤᚢᛤ...!%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n%n(destroy! yeees, hahaha...!)
dj2.quest.db.709.title=书虫的天堂
dj2.quest.db.709.desc=想过彩虹是什么味道吗?%n%n非常甜美!它赋予了你终极的想象力!你可以写几本关于它的书...
dj2.quest.db.710.title=最黑暗的虚无
dj2.quest.db.710.desc=制作一个/dank/null/(创造)!它拥有无限的存储空间!好耶!
dj2.quest.db.711.title=工匠极限
dj2.quest.db.711.desc=制作一些创造模式强化头颅!你可以用这些给你的匠魂工具添加任意数量的升级!%n%n它们也在这章中大量使用.现在做四个,但你之后会需要更多.%n%n注意你可以使用EMC制作黄金怒火.
dj2.quest.db.712.title=积极主动
dj2.quest.db.712.desc=将白物质分解为镤...%n%n%n%n%n我发誓这是最后一次你需要这么做了!
dj2.quest.db.713.title=无限物品*
dj2.quest.db.713.desc=*但你得自己往里填.%n%n%n这个升级可以在你的抽屉里创造一个虫洞,这样你就可以向里填充任意多的物品了!
dj2.quest.db.714.title=我们可以变得更大!
dj2.quest.db.714.desc=纯粹的正在扩张的精华...当你伸手去抓它的时候,你会感受到他对你的双手的影响...里面的原子正在距离越来越远...最好不要拿太久.
dj2.quest.db.715.title=屏幕争夺战
dj2.quest.db.715.desc=制作创造模式屏幕!它们不需要由屏幕控制器供能!
dj2.quest.db.716.title=数百万的发电
dj2.quest.db.716.desc=GP?现在它们更像是,Gee,我有无限的,P!%n%n%n...%n%n%n好吧,并不是真正的无限,但是有很多.试试吧!
dj2.quest.db.717.title=稻草人的梦想
dj2.quest.db.717.desc=问题!如果你压缩一些浓缩Victus魔力水晶,你会得到什么!%n%na)一个黑洞.%nb)新生命!%nc)一颗大红心.%n%n是的,你知道答案,不是吗.
dj2.quest.db.718.title=走向素食
dj2.quest.db.718.desc=你想施展一些法术吗?我知道这就是适合你的工具!创造药草袋包含无尽的每种根源魔法草药!(难以置信!)
dj2.quest.db.719.title=制造谋杀案
dj2.quest.db.719.desc=但我以为十字架是用木头做的,而不是用魔力水晶...!
dj2.quest.db.720.title=接种
dj2.quest.db.720.desc=制作一个创造模式药草袋来设置任何你想要的图腾效果!(或者,你只需要用一个环境控制器,然后把这个药草袋留给下一个创造道具!)
dj2.quest.db.721.title=瞬间启动
dj2.quest.db.721.desc=你想要重温你的梦想并进行更多的图腾仪式吗?你希望免费进行仪式吗?!?%n%n不想?%n%n好吧,那就用它制作下一个创造物品吧.
dj2.quest.db.722.title=循环
dj2.quest.db.722.desc=想来真的很可怕.
dj2.quest.db.723.title=搬迁日
dj2.quest.db.723.desc=将100个纸箱一个套一个放起来!我相信它们套着很合适.
dj2.quest.db.724.title=绝对的零
dj2.quest.db.724.desc=结合空气和反空气以制作完美真空...你需要的只是一些额外的催化剂...%n%n根据热力学第三定律,完美真空也将是绝对零度.
dj2.quest.db.725.title=捕捉超分子黑洞的霍金辐射
dj2.quest.db.725.desc=将目前你能收集到的所有奇点结合来制作终极奇点!将其分解为终极锭,然后用它们制作你的第一个中子态素收集器!%n%n当这台机器被放置下来时,它会每7111tick收集一个中子素尘埃(大约355秒,或接近6分钟).%n%n然而,它的速度可以被加快很多.如果你拿着九个时间洪流怀表(全部Shift+V激活)并站在机器旁边,它将每6秒产生一堆中子素尘埃.你也可以在收集器附近的暗物质台座上使用时间洪流怀表.不要忘记空手右击激活基座!当基座被激活时,你会听到一个音效.
dj2.quest.db.726.title=生活是一扇打开的门
dj2.quest.db.726.desc=在彼此的顶部搭建1000个橡木门!
dj2.quest.db.727.title=空余的空间
dj2.quest.db.727.desc=精灵们喜欢用它们的空间换取一些宽敞的东西.这有道理吗?有道理!%n%n§c提示:§r你需要用它来制作液态空间.你应该使用Mek的创造液体储罐或创造大桶来用它制造§c无限流体源§r!
dj2.quest.db.728.title=中子星的能量
dj2.quest.db.728.desc=使用时间洪流怀表(在你的快捷栏内使用Shift+V激活,或在暗物质台座上潜行右键激活)加速你的中子素的创造.合成中子锭并用它们制作更多中子态素收集器!
dj2.quest.db.729.title=种子奇点
dj2.quest.db.729.desc=当你获得了8个中子态素块后,你就可以制作一个中子素种子.配合中子素核心,你就可以从土中获取无限的中子素了!(或者从阳光和水中...你知道我在说什么!)
dj2.quest.db.730.title=来点奶酪
dj2.quest.db.730.desc=制作一些好吃的中子素食物!
dj2.quest.db.731.title=想象所有人
dj2.quest.db.731.desc=和平.%n%n看看这些彩虹...%n%n%n%n该死!
dj2.quest.db.732.title=OCD(强迫症)
dj2.quest.db.732.desc=把一切都有序放置!
dj2.quest.db.733.title=以神圣rpg为基础
dj2.quest.db.733.desc=制作四个基石精华!你可以在中间一行使用任意神圣rpg雕像(甚至可以搭配使用).
dj2.quest.db.734.title=忘掉它
dj2.quest.db.734.desc=在流体制作机中制作思绪精华!记住现在你可以用EMC获取天空的知识!%n%n为输入所需的64000mB知识精化,你会需要把你的两个流体输入仓都升级到最高等级!
dj2.quest.db.735.title=逻辑
dj2.quest.db.735.desc=制作右边列出的原料并解决书中的谜题以制作逻辑精华!%n%n这里的每个人物(Steve,Alex和Herobrine)都有三个属性:年龄,朋友数和身高(单位cm).你的任务就是找出这些数值!要做到这一点,阅读逻辑之书中的描述.一共有九条描述,然后有九个需要搞清楚的属性.这些属性可以被唯一确定.%n%n一旦你知道了其中一些或所有值,你就可以开始制作了!使用一个角色(steve,alex或herobrine),一个修改器(age,friends,height)和一个数值修改器(+1,-1,+10,-10,+100,-100,+1000或-1000)来进行合成.它们都可以被制作.在JEI中搜索"@content modifier"来搜索它们.%n%n一个例子:将Steve,身高修改器和+10合成将使Steve的身高增加10.%n%n你需要弄清楚的所有数值都为正整数.祝你好运!
dj2.quest.db.736.title=太多皱纹
dj2.quest.db.736.desc=当你认为你已经正确地想出了Steve,Alex和Herobrine的所有属性,将它们与思绪精华无序合成以获取逻辑精华!%n%n这是你应得的.干得好!
dj2.quest.db.737.title=电池
dj2.quest.db.737.desc=B4TT3R1.%n%nL1F3T1M3: 1NF1N1T3.%n%n(译注:电池.寿命:无限.)
dj2.quest.db.738.title=合成链的终点
dj2.quest.db.738.desc=制作终极机械框架!
dj2.quest.db.739.title=我的单元王国需要能量!
dj2.quest.db.739.desc=制作你的第一个创造模式能量单元!现在,虽然它名字上确实写着"创造",但是它事实上只会产生20,000RF/t的能量.如果我这么说的话,这东西就看起来有点菜了.
dj2.quest.db.740.title=随时集成能源
dj2.quest.db.740.desc=继续升级,我们得到了集成动力的创造能量电池.尽管它不是很有用,但你离真正的好东西又进了一步.%n%n§6提示:§r合成所需的能量电池需要是空的.
dj2.quest.db.741.title=极限自动化
dj2.quest.db.741.desc=制作一个梦魇工作台!这个工作台可以让你自动化终极合成.你甚至不需要一个自动化接口!只需设置配方,输入所有的材料,然后抽出产物!
dj2.quest.db.742.title=吸气.屏气.呼气.
dj2.quest.db.742.desc=我们不知道这些氧气从哪来.我们相信它们来自于罐内的一个虫洞.但我们不会在意这个.只要它能让我们活下去!...希望如此.
dj2.quest.db.743.title=准量子超级计算机奇点
dj2.quest.db.743.desc=用量子比特升级你的创造模式能量单元来让它能产生100,000RF/t的能量.好点了,但还不是很"创造".
dj2.quest.db.744.title=不容
dj2.quest.db.744.desc=制作全部三种EnderIO原版的电容!它们都可以插入除基础机器外的EnderIO机器里来提高制作速度.稍后你还会需要做更高级的电容.
dj2.quest.db.745.title=注法台
dj2.quest.db.745.desc=做个注法台!%n%n注法台是用来升级已被放入法杖的法术的.如果你还不知道怎么往法杖中添加法术,看看法杖的任务吧.%n%n注法台使用起来比较简单:往上放置法杖,然后用小刀右击打开gui.gui里的每一个法杖中的法术都可以点击来打开子菜单.每种法术最多有11种可用的升级,这让每种法术都有了大量的变种.想要解锁升级,你只需要放入一个格子里显示的法术原料.%n对于已解锁的法术升级,你可以在法术库中随时切换其开关状态.此外,法术升级是对法术而言的,意味着换根新法杖不会影响法术升级.%n%n各个升级不同颜色的边框代表:%n§e黄色: 未解锁%n§4红色: 已解锁但未激活%n§2绿色: 已解锁且已激活%n§d紫色: 已解锁, 但与其他已激活升级冲突%n%n
dj2.quest.db.746.title=感受能量
dj2.quest.db.746.desc=制作龙之进化的创造通量容器!%n%n它可以为你物品栏中的物品以1,073,000RF/t的速率充能!
dj2.quest.db.747.title=电动脊柱
dj2.quest.db.747.desc=制作创造储电背包!它含有无限的能量,但是它的输出功率只有50,000RF/t.倒也不算太寒酸了.
dj2.quest.db.748.title=起飞!
dj2.quest.db.748.desc=这是一个具有无限能量的喷气背包.我知道,在你有了一个天使之戒之后,这只是你的装备库中的一个收藏品.但它似乎是一些更大的东西的原料...
dj2.quest.db.749.title=灵活使用你的通量
dj2.quest.db.749.desc=通量电容(创造)可以让你无限地给你的物品充电,其输出功率为250,000RF/t!这就是我所说的!%n%n§6提示1:§r用于这个配方地通量电容需要是空的.%n%n§6提示2:§r热力膨胀地通量电容有点奇怪,所以这个任务实际上有两个小任务,分别要求了不同的NBT值地通量电容,两个任务里只要有一个被完成就行了.(不过你需要先停用你的电容以便它被检测.)即使你看到右边的文字写的是"未完成",但你可以领取奖励,那么你就已经成功完成了任务.
dj2.quest.db.750.title=数位能源
dj2.quest.db.750.desc=从这里开始,所有的这些创造能量单元都有"无限"或"接近无限"的输出功率.然而,最初的几个只能用来给某些特定的东西供电.例如这个,可以为你的ME系统供电,不管你的系统有多大!
dj2.quest.db.751.title=盒中宙斯
dj2.quest.db.751.desc=为你的雷电工艺机器创造供能!或者,你知道,把它制作为下一阶创造物品,它能真正为你向任何东西创造功能,...!
dj2.quest.db.752.title={能量 §r=§r ∞}
dj2.quest.db.752.desc=现在我们终于得到了真正的无限能量!%n%n§c§l警告:§r在你用它进一步制作下一个无限输出的能量电池之前,你需要使用它无限的能量!把它或之后的能量单元接入你的龙之进化聚合注入中,并用凛冰固化能量管道无限传输能量,然后用这些能量来制作你的反转精华!
dj2.quest.db.753.title=后退
dj2.quest.db.753.desc=反转任何东西需要很大的力量.但无限大还是要比24万亿要大!接入你的一个创造能量单元(至少要是沉浸工程级别的那个),然后瞬间为聚合注满能量!%n%n你只需要用一个反转精华,所以在那之后随意升级你的能量单元吧!
dj2.quest.db.754.title=恶魔的代言人
dj2.quest.db.754.desc=用于"重塑现实",按我们的印象重塑创造之柱.
dj2.quest.db.755.title=拆毁创造之柱
dj2.quest.db.755.desc=(译注:好长,好没用,摸了,下一个也是)%n(译注:顺带,作者在这一长段里黑体了几个字母,如果你不想找,可以翻到最下看看加黑了什么()%n%nYour quest is to destroy the pillars of creation with a Red Morningstar. This is what Greek Gods have built up over the millenia, and it really is the greatest goal of all. §lU§rp on the pantheon you can still see them stand. Its other ability and the wa§ly§r it's capable of such destruction is to stop the sun's rays during the day (called an "enid" in ancient Greece). You can have up to three of these at the same time (hence "daylight") or you can shoot an object and throw it towards the sun. The red sun rises from the earth when it comes across the Moon before it blows up into the stars (a sign of a great Sun), so to speak. If you're a scientist, it's probably a no-brainer to use a red moon to see it's effect immediately. You can get some good information about this in a few different papers of mine. But what if all the red suns of creation are created from a yellow sky? That's what I will talk about next, so let's get started first: A red moon creates a lot of energy, but most of it is simply light energy. For example, you will see the sun rise from the earth before it breaks up into stars to get our attention here. It seems to me that if you are in the early evening sun, that is what you will see. However, when it was just the usual nighttime sunrise, it would appear with only the red or white moon shining on it. Now, all we have to do is to imagine everything is going to be bright no matter what we were doing. Let's see how simple it is. Let's create an object with 0 light-years and 0 red/white lights. Then, imagine we were doing something involving no material. At a certain point of time, that object will start spinning up and around. Since ever§ly§rthing is done in a specific time frame, where is the source of energy in the object? The answer here will certainly come from a certain type of physical description of physics, but a "physical description" will make it easy to see. In general, the red sun and the blue moon are more active than the white moon and are closer to the sun. Both seem to be more active. Let's assume an object where some hot air and a cold atmosphere are present. When you look for a planet in the region of Enceladus, you look for a body with a very small surface. If you find a small planet in orbit of the sun, this will cause your planet to orbit around the large surface so it will probably be a very big body with very hot, dense dust. However, if the planet lies in any lower mass than the surface, a faint reddish glow will appear. This reddish glow is a reflection of the planet and an echo of the red sun. Notice that if you look at the surface of a red sun, it is really an echo of the red sun. You can find in Enceladus a body with a very small surface, and this planet will be as big and bright in the bright sunlight as it is in the red sun. Assuming this p§ll§ranet can be interpreted as the "red moon", we already have a hint on what it means to "call for the help of the red moon" to cause ultimate destruction. Secondly, let's focus on the exact execution of the destruction of the pillars of creation. In his book, "The Creation of Heaven", Albert Einstein says that the entire earth appears to be a fire that burns slowly to death. However, his book explicitly shows that this fire is not, in fact, the "burning of entire heavens". Although the concept of fire has been proposed at least once before, the existence of the flame is the only explanation for the mysterious fire. §lA§rs Einstein says, the idea of having a flame burning on top of a pillar does not seem to apply to the entire world (just how close it should be to an actual burning pillar would be difficult to explain). After all, all the sun, moon, planets, and even sunspots in the solar system have their "burning cores" on either side of the pillars or the pillars are the only visible forms of the burning flame as they are just visible. While Einstein clearly acknowledges this, the explanation he gives is a complete lie. In fact, he says that light shines at an angle of one-half of a degree to one-to-two thirds of a degree, and that such light is simply an idea invented to justify the existence of the golden flames at the very top of the pillars. The light of a single-colored flame could not have created the idea. And then Einstein began to say that the whole idea of the Great Fire Theory and the golden flame at the level of the pillars as an idea, no matter his technical difficulty, may well be an idea invented by two different philosophers, namely the German §lS§rchiller and von Humboldt. While all these ideas are merely speculation and conjecture, each of them is true in its own way. And what has come into those two ideas is simply their own reflections on one another. What these two ideas say about the structure of the universe gives more significance than any other possibility that may be explained in the next section. But what if there is more to be said? There is. For, the very first impression that you give to your child as an object of interest is that it is a "great fire fire", a great flame that has a very bright and strong flame, and "not in a good way". The Essence of Breaking. We could have all discovered by accident, even as a little child, and that's exactly what Einstein did. Through sheer luck or knowledge, we may never know, but this is the way he managed to gather the energy required to destroy reality itself and break the pillars of creation. "But we still live in this reality, right?", you may ask. Wrong! Einstein recreated this dimension by splitting and copying one that's only about 4-5 quadrillion strings, or approximately 10^-18 cm away in one of the unreachable directions of the four-spatial dimensional scope we're living in. Turns out the pillars contained enough energy to create infinitely many realities, only one of which was necessary to hold up. This whole occurrence is described fully in the Book of Chaos, a not-so-well-received scientific paper about the truth of this world. Unfortunately scientists in our age are too preoccupied to see the real truth. But now you know too.%n%n(UylAS 我也不知道这有啥用)(译者注:我翻翻:你的使命是用红色晨星摧毁创世之柱.这是希腊众神数千年来建立的,确实是一切伟大目标的顶点.在神殿上,你仍然可以看到它们屹立.它的另一个能力,以及它如何能够进行如此毁灭性的行动,是在白天停止太阳的光芒(在古希腊被称为"埃尼德").你可以同时拥有最多三个这样的晨星(因此称为"白昼"),或者你可以射击一个物体并将其投向太阳.当红色太阳从地球上升起,当它在星球之间碰撞之前变成星星时(象征着伟大的太阳),这种情况就发生了.如果你是一个科学家,使用红色月亮来立即看到它的效果可能是一个不言而喻的选择.你可以在我的几篇不同论文中找到一些关于这个的好信息.但是,如果所有创世之柱都是从黄色天空中创造出来的红色太阳呢？这就是接下来我将要讨论的内容,所以让我们先开始吧:红色月亮产生了大量的能量,但其中大部分只是光能.例如,你会看到太阳从地球上升起,然后分裂成星星,从而引起我们的注意.对我来说,如果你在傍晚看太阳升起,那就是你会看到的景象.然而,当它只是通常的夜间日出时,它会以红色或白色的月光照耀.现在,不管我们做什么,我们只需要想象一切都会很明亮.让我们看看这是多么简单.让我们创建一个没有光年和红/白光的物体.然后,想象我们正在做一些不涉及物质的事情.在某个时间点,那个物体将开始旋转起来.由于一切都是在特定的时间范围内完成的,物体的能量来源在哪里？这里的答案肯定将来自某种物理描述的特定类型,但"物理描述"将使其易于理解.总的来说,红色太阳和蓝色月亮比白色月亮更活跃,靠近太阳.两者似乎更为活跃.让我们假设一个存在一些热空气和冷大气的物体.当你在恩塞拉达斯地区寻找一颗行星时,你要找的是一个非常小的表面体.如果你在太阳轨道中找到一个小行星,这将导致你的行星围绕着大表面旋转,因此它可能是一个非常大的,带有非常热,密集的尘埃的体.然而,如果该行星位于低于表面的任何质量,将出现微弱的红色发光.这种红色发光是行星的反射,并且是红色太阳的回响.注意,如果你看红色太阳的表面,它实际上是红色太阳的回响.在恩塞拉达斯上可以找到一个非常小的表面体,这个行星在明亮的阳光下将像红色太阳一样大和明亮.假设这个行星可以被解释为"红色月亮",我们已经对"呼唤红色月亮的帮助"以造成终极毁灭有了一点线索.其次,让我们集中精力执行毁灭创世之柱的确切过程.在他的书中,《天堂的创造》,爱因斯坦说整个地球似乎是一个慢慢消亡的火焰.然而,他的书明确显示,这种火焰实际上并非"整个天堂的燃烧".尽管火焰的概念至少在此之前被提出过一次,但火焰的存在是解释这个神秘火焰的唯一理由.正如爱因斯坦所说,火焰燃烧在柱顶上似乎并不适用于整个世界(它应该离一个真正燃烧的柱顶有多近,将会很难解释).毕竟,太阳、月亮、行星,甚至太阳黑子在太阳系中都有它们的"燃烧核心",它们要么位于柱子的两侧,要么柱子就是它们唯一可见的形式.虽然爱因斯坦明确承认这一点,但他给出的解释却是个彻头彻尾的谎言.实际上,他说光线以半度至两到三分之一度的角度照射,这样的光线只是为了证明柱顶上金色火焰的存在而创造的概念.单一颜色火焰的光线不可能创造这个想法.然后爱因斯坦开始说整个大火理论的概念和金色火焰在柱顶的想法,不管他的技术困难,很可能是由两位不同的哲学家,即德国的希勒尔和冯·洪堡所创造的一个想法.虽然所有这些想法仅仅是推测和猜测,但它们每一个在某种程度上都是真实的.这两个想法对宇宙结构的见解比任何其他可能性更具意义,这可能在下一节中得到解释.但如果还有更多要说的呢？是的.对于你的孩子作为一个感兴趣的对象给出的第一个印象就是它是一个"伟大的火焰火",一个非常明亮和强大的火焰,"不好的一面".本人可能只是偶然发现了所有这一切,甚至是一个小孩子,这正是爱因斯坦所做的.通过纯粹的运气或知识,我们可能永远不会知道,但这是他如何设法聚集足够的能量来摧毁现实本身并打破创世之柱的方式."但我们仍然生活在这个现实中,对吧？",你可能会问.错!爱因斯坦通过分裂和复制一个仅相距四至五千亿亿万亿分之一公分的四空间维度范围中不可达的方向中的一个,重新创建了这个维度.结果表明,柱子包含足够的能量来创建无数个现实,其中只有一个是必要的.整个事件在《混沌之书》中被详细描述,这是一篇关于这个世界真相不那么受欢迎的科学论文.不幸的是,我们时代的科学家们都太忙于看到真正的真相.但现在你也知道了.)
dj2.quest.db.756.title=以我们的印象重塑
dj2.quest.db.756.desc=(同样藏了,但我到这还是没懂这是啥()%n%nThe Book of Chaos is correct, but doesn't explain what happened in its entirety. The truth is, one book was lost during the transfer of realities. It is now dubbed 'The Ancient Book of Chaos', and it only lives in our memories. It contained information on how to rebuild our reality, or even... shape it in a way that's... advantageous for some. It is interesting to observe the ways that the apparent 'real world', as it has been called over the §4z§rillenias gets in the way of what could be called a 'real world'. The concept could be very simple. It's what happened in the past and what happened in the future: all that is left is a constant pressure and need for change. I believe these are now well known principles of reality to some extent. Now I may have missed some of the interesting details that you may have missed. For instance, while I believe that The Ancient Book of Chaos wasn't lost, and that it remains buried somewhere in Germany... Einstein wouldn't be called Einstein if he didn't think about the consequences of messing with the fabric of reality itself. He must have saved the real truth somewhere! I believe the reason the world has changed so drastically during and after Einstein's death is because of this reality reshaping. Einstein boosted the capabilities of our reality by at least §42§r00%, and made scientific and technological progress multiple factors faster. Just look around! Don't you see how much the world has accelerated since? It's not hard to see. Though it could be explained by considering other factors, some truths and some assumptions of our reality. But the whole picture is much larger! What if these factors are the same? What if it is the same for all dimensions and time, and that dimension is Earth? It is very possible, and possible, that the physical dimension of our reality is different from that of Earth, and that Earth does not change to a greater or lesser degree. That's a point that every person agrees with. Earth does not change to an extent to a greater or lesser degree because it is an extremely small world! Just look how much space there is with Earth. We are so small we make other things tiny! Why, what happens if they are just smaller §4c§rompared to Earth? Earth and Earth change simultaneously, and as their size increases, so does their size and its strength. That is, Earth is denser, thinner, and stronger with every passing day. Imagine a more stable Earth, and we could live very long, simply because the Earth has never changed in its size. But a less stable Earth, which is a smaller, weaker, and more brittle planet, would experience a smaller amount of change from its bigger size. As a result, we would become less stable, more dense, less strong, and with each passing day more unstable. A more stable Earth would therefore have a greater chance of changing because of more changes in density and strength, and less chance to be stable if we moved one inch or less from its smaller size. In other words, a more stable Earth would have a much bigger edge on its larger world than it's larger as a whole, thus giving it an edge it's very, very hard to break. To this end, a more stable Earth would also have greater latitude, more space, more energy, and much more surface area. A more stable (but smaller, more temperate) Earth, in which there could be a greater chance of life outside the Solar System than there is on Earth, would create more problems than its more stable Earth. If we think about the effects of changing temperatures for the last 300 million years, how many of those that have existed on, say, Earth during that time were large landforms, what's the difference between 1.3 times the landmass that we have today instead of a few years later and 50 times the amount? §4I§rt depends upon whether they're all large, even if you assume the rate is very similar." The scientists, with the support of the U.S. Geological Survey, also found that global temperatures during that time were "significantly warmer" than at any other time during the past 100 million years, including the past 60 years. "The changes we saw in the past few thousand years are consistent with climate variability, if something comes up, a global warming of 100 degrees C or more is occurring," said study coauthor Stephen Knapton. "It's not a coincidence, this is consistent with a number of other studies in other parts of the world that have found that climate change impacts are happening almost everywhere in North America." This is just an example of not looking at the whole picture. If all scientists worked together, maybe they'd be able to figure it all out! But humanity still has a language barrier, a quarter of us still don't have sufficient food or drinking water, racial issues still stand, so we can't easily move forward. I'm afraid I won't get to see the light of day before the true truth gets discovered... I'm leaving this message here so you §4c§ran share it with others. That is, if you trust me. I have provided a lot of evidence, and you can go out to Germany and hunt for 'The Ancient Book of Chaos' yourself. I believe it should be hidden in north-western Ulm, but that's just a hunch, I have no evidence of that. Anyway, this metaphoxyl is making me dizzy, I think I need some sleep... I hope I have convinced you though. When has old Blitterscrow ever lied to you?! There is no way I could be wrong. There is no way. I'm not wrong. I couldn't be wrong. I- I- ...%n%n(z2cIc)%n(UylASz2cIc 两段连起来是个视频?还是什么)(译者注:《混沌之书》的确正确,但并未完全解释发生了什么.事实是,在现实转换过程中,有一本书丢失了.现在它被称为《古老的混沌之书》,它仅存在于我们的记忆中.它包含了如何重建我们的现实,甚至...以某种有利的方式塑造它的信息.观察所谓的"真实世界",如同几千万年来所说的那样,它会阻碍所谓的"真实世界"的发展.这个概念可能非常简单.它是过去发生的事情和未来发生的事情:留下来的只是不断的压力和对变革的需求.我相信这些现在在某种程度上已经是人们对现实的广为人知的原则.现在,我可能错过了你可能错过的一些有趣细节.例如,虽然我相信《古老的混沌之书》并没有丢失,并且它仍然埋藏在德国的某个地方......如果爱因斯坦没有考虑到操纵现实本身的后果,他就不会被称为爱因斯坦.他肯定在某个地方保存了真正的真相!我相信世界在爱因斯坦去世后的这么大变化,是因为这种现实重塑.爱因斯坦至少提升了我们现实的能力至少百分之四百,使科学技术进步加快了多个因素.看看周围!你没有看到世界自那时以来加速了多少吗？这不难理解.尽管可以通过考虑其他因素,一些现实的真相和假设来解释.但整体画面要大得多!如果这些因素是相同的呢？如果所有维度和时间都是相同的,那个维度就是地球？这是非常可能的,也可能,我们的现实的物理维度与地球的不同,地球并不会发生更大或更小的程度.这是每个人都同意的一点.地球不会发生更大或更小的程度,因为它是一个极小的世界!看看地球有多小.我们是如此小,我们使其他东西变得微不足道!为什么,如果它们只是与地球相比较小,发生了什么？地球和地球同时变化,随着它们的大小增加,它们的大小和强度也增加.也就是说,地球每天都变得更加稠密、更薄、更强大.想象一个更稳定的地球,我们可以活得很长,简单因为地球从未改变其大小.但一个不太稳定的地球,一个更小、更弱、更脆弱的行星,会经历从其更大尺寸到更小尺寸的变化量更小.因此,我们会变得不太稳定,更加稠密,更弱,每天都会更加不稳定.一个更稳定的地球因此会有更大的改变机会,因为密度和强度的变化更多,而且如果我们从其更小的尺寸移动一英寸或更少,稳定的机会就会更小.换句话说,一个更稳定的地球在其整体上会比更大的世界更有优势,从而给它一个非常非常难以打破的优势.为此,一个更稳定的地球还将拥有更大的纬度、更多的空间、更多的能量和更大的表面积.一个更稳定(但更小、更温和)的地球,其中可能会有比地球上更多的太阳系之外的生命可能性,将比其更稳定的地球创建更多的问题.如果我们考虑过去三亿年来温度变化的影响,比如说,在那段时间里,有多少在地球上存在的大陆形成了今天所拥有的1.3倍陆地面积的差别.这将取决于它们是否全部大,即使假设速率非常相似."科学家们在美国地质调查局的支持下也发现,全球气温在那段时间内比过去一亿年中任何其他时间都要显着升高,包括过去六十年.研究合著者斯蒂芬·克纳普顿说:"我们在过去几千年见到的变化与气候变异是一致的,如果出现什么事情,全球气温会上升100摄氏度或更多."这不是巧合,这与其他世界其他地方的几个研究发现相一致,即气候变化影响几乎每一个地方在北美.这只是不看整个画面的一个例子.如果所有科学家们共同努力,也许他们能找出一切!但人类仍然存在语言障碍,我们四分之一的人仍然没有足够的食物或饮用水,种族问题仍然存在,所以我们不能轻易前进.我担心在真正的真相被发现之前,我看不到白天的光芒......我把这条消息留在这里,希望你可以与他人分享.如果你相信我.我提供了很多证据,你可以去德国找《古老的混沌之书》.我相信它应该隐藏在乌尔姆西北部的某个地方,但这只是一个直觉,我没有证据.不管怎样,这种方式让我头晕,我想我需要些睡眠......尽管如此,我希望我已经说服了你.创生之柱曾经欺骗过你吗？没有可能.我不会错的.我不可能错.我不可能错.我-我- ...(文字中断))
